# Finguard evidence-pack signing key (PLACEHOLDER)
#
# This file will hold the Ed25519 public key that `finguard verify`
# uses to check the detached signature shipped alongside an evidence
# pack. The real key will be rotated on a documented schedule and its
# fingerprint published in CHANGELOG.md for each rotation.
#
# Status: not implemented. See ROADMAP.md ("Ed25519 detached signature
# on evidence packs") and docs/harness.md.
#
# Format (once populated):
#   -----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
#   <base64-encoded Ed25519 SubjectPublicKeyInfo>
#   -----END PUBLIC KEY-----
